MiCraft
-------

Minecraft map viewer by Bertrand Chazot
PLNC 2011
Télécom ParisTech
______________________________________________________

Camera:
	-Z/Q/S/D: move
	-Right/Left/Up/Down or mouse: look around
	-Page up: move up
	-Page down: move down
	-A: activate/desactivate vertical motion with Z/S

Tool:
	F1: highlight coal ore
	F2: highlight iron ore
	F3: highlight gold ore
	F4: highlight diamond ore
	F5: highlight lapis lazuli ore
	F6: highlight redstone ore
	F7: highlight obsidian
	F8: highlight clay

Other:
	P: pause/unpause
	M: more chunks drawn
	L: less chunks drawn
